name: Rak_Jaren
content:
Rak Jaren was a Human male who worked as a bounty hunter. He was a refugee from his homeworld of Subterrel. Nicknamed "Shadow Hunter", Jaren had a companion named Kellic.
Rak Jaren was the final name of the main protagonist in the early phases  of the cancelled LucasArts game Star Wars: 1313. Earlier in development, his name was Ty Gerra. His companion in the trailer was named Kellic. This information was all confirmed in a tweet by Matt Boland, who credited 1313's Creative Director, Dominic Robilliard, with the information. No other information is known.
